Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:43.04,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,Pare de ser um bebê chorão!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.36,Main,Random Soldier,0,0,0,,Pare de ser louco!
