Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.33,Main,Monet,0,0,0,,Mas pode não ser o caso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.00,0:18:41.67,Main,Marines,0,0,0,,Há outro quarto nos fundos!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.67,0:18:44.74,Main,Marines,0,0,0,,Vamos encontrar as crianças e sair daqui!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.74,0:18:46.43,Main,Marines,0,0,0,,Não está meio frio aqui?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.43,0:18:47.66,Main,Zoro,0,0,0,,A Marinha?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:50.17,Main,Sanji,0,0,0,,{ Btwb: Sounds like Sanji, so I changed the actor. }Vamos passar por aquela porta ali atrás!
